Description: simple histogram tool producing text dot-matrix graphs
 This tool lets you plot a single-series histogram on a text dot-matrix
 display by abusing Unicode.  This gives a resolution of 2Ã—4 per character,
 as opposed to the usual single asterisk you get with ASCII.
